data.description: Welcome to the experience of being wrapped in Colorado beauty. The 4 bedroom 3 bath home sits at the base of Old Man Mountain. This serene setting with large decks amongst the aspens and ponderosas plus the sight and sounds of Fall River will heighten your senses. The many windows, and glass doors bring the light, blue bird skies in. Stepping inside you are struck by the warmth from the knotty alder cabinets, wood and beamed ceilings, and moss rock fireplaces. This property, also, features radiant heat, providing an efficient and effective way to keep the living space warm during colder months. This home offers room for all your family and friends with the large living room, with a moss rock floor to ceiling fireplace, a rec room plus multiple decks to gather. The kitchen is upgraded with knotty alder cabinets, a gas stovetop island, breakfast bar and ample counter space for meal preparation. A large walk in pantry is steps away with abundant storage. The dining area is perfect for family gatherings or entertaining guests. Or everyone can move to the deck for al fresco dining. There is nice, level outdoor space for games and relaxing. With this home's comfortable living spaces, and outdoor decks, and location this home offers an opportunity to experience a peaceful, beautiful and relaxing Colorado lifestyle.
